  "instructions": [
    "Heat sesame oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add diced ginger and sauté for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add gochujang and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add Korean chili flakes, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add sliced radish and cook for 3-4 minutes until it starts to soften.",
    "Add sliced cabbage and cook for an additional 2-3 minutes until it starts to wilt.",
    "Add red snapper fillets and cook for 2-3 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "Add doenjang and stir to combine.",
    "Add water and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10-15 minutes or until the stew has thickened slightly.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with sesame seeds and sliced radish.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
